sequenceDiagram
    participant CA as ClientA
    participant CB as ClientB
    participant SRV as DocActor
    participant LOG as OpLog
    participant SNAP as SnapshotStore

    Note over SRV: Single-threaded actor per doc_id
    CA->>SRV: op{insert 'x' @ pos10, rev=R}
    Note over SRV: server already at rev R+5
    SRV->>SRV: OT transform op against missed ops [R+1..R+5]
    SRV->>SRV: apply transformed op -> rev R+6
    SRV->>LOG: append (rev R+6, transformed_op)
    SRV-->>CA: ack{server_rev=R+6}
    SRV-)CB: remote_op{ops', rev=R+6}
    CB->>CB: apply remote op locally

    Note over CB: concurrent local edit
    CB->>SRV: op{delete range, rev=R+6}
    SRV->>SRV: apply (no transform needed, on tip)
    SRV->>LOG: append (rev R+7)
    SRV-->>CB: ack{server_rev=R+7}
    SRV-)CA: remote_op{rev=R+7}

    Note over SRV,SNAP: every N ops
    SRV-)SNAP: persist snapshot(doc, rev=R+7)
    SRV->>LOG: GC ops < snapshot rev
